[{"id":"0197149f-9422-72de-af27-b6817c4a00a7","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":21626,"content":"22 年的时候面过，说是强制加班","createdAt":"2025-05-28T10:01:31"},{"id":"01971597-e94a-727a-96b1-55ac1bd13346","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":21396,"content":"成分就是这样，狗改不了吃屎，你还能指望他自己良心发现变好么","createdAt":"2025-05-28T14:32:46"},{"id":"01971a0d-2350-72d9-869d-4945a842c28e","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":5661,"content":"听说莱易是外包，相同年限是不是工资会比自研的高不少？","createdAt":"2025-05-29T11:19:18"},{"id":"01971aa0-d3a1-72c9-8211-92358dbcd3d6","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":24599,"content":"1","createdAt":"2025-05-29T14:00:37"},{"id":"01971fd5-e6df-707e-a89f-ecceaa5583b9","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":21364,"content":"那为啥还在招新人，听说还有烟草的项目","createdAt":"2025-05-30T14:16:41"},{"id":"01971fd8-9cf5-73b6-a1fb-95213a70110f","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":21364,"content":"同问，，","createdAt":"2025-05-30T14:19:39"},{"id":"019733d3-8799-7172-8fde-4d01a18aeea3","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":22186,"content":"外包就是这样啊，有的好项目不累的就不招人了，那种不好的，人流动大的肯定不停的招人","createdAt":"2025-06-03T11:26:30"},{"id":"019733d4-f42f-71aa-92e0-9c078ed5ea81","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":22186,"content":"不能这么说，外包也看项目上给的钱多少，总体来说，外包主要是看项目上预算多少，他们在看你的要求多少，中间吃一层","createdAt":"2025-06-03T11:28:03"},{"id":"01974f39-cce3-71b4-8930-73d6b0b7f8b0","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":21460,"content":"现在的加班情况咋样","createdAt":"2025-06-08T19:07:57"},{"id":"01975244-cd4b-7041-a466-a169f639640b","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":22186,"content":"不一定，看项目上，跟莱易关系不大，除了发工资，请假，其余的以项目为准，浪潮加班反正，懂得都懂","createdAt":"2025-06-09T09:18:50"},{"id":"019753cd-fb26-70e0-8594-73319f407063","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":21364,"content":"老哥，我朋友进去试岗了，为啥全是新来的，到现在都没咋见老人儿，而且还在招人，不能是白嫖仨月试用期的吧，慌啊","createdAt":"2025-06-09T16:28:17"},{"id":"019753d4-501f-7209-afba-925114a5c4bc","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":22186,"content":"外派到哪了，也不好说，莱易只是负责人事，具体的都得看项目上，项目上说明天裁，莱易就裁，他就相当于发工资和人事，请假之类的，你得问问你们项目上为什么没有老人，打听一下","createdAt":"2025-06-09T16:35:12"},{"id":"019753d6-61a1-73c7-a8cb-a93d6f55d6de","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":22186,"content":"不好说，看你外派的项目","createdAt":"2025-06-09T16:37:28"},{"id":"0197576d-ec02-7097-b9f9-38c224cb5dfd","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":21364,"content":"还没分清是什么项目，身边除了组长就没有转正的，都是试用期，问不上。先干着","createdAt":"2025-06-10T09:21:51"},{"id":"01975870-97bc-731d-a70f-980174d8f407","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":22186,"content":"在哪个地方上班","createdAt":"2025-06-10T14:04:23"},{"id":"0197a572-15d6-72c7-9525-2161c35fab67","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":1225,"content":"现在还在莱易吗","createdAt":"2025-06-25T12:56:46"},{"id":"0197a611-3e90-7122-bd16-5f1d36316a90","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":22186,"content":"在啊，在外包上","createdAt":"2025-06-25T15:50:37"},{"id":"0197f27a-78d5-7008-b16d-08325a11b624","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":22063,"content":"孙村那边的外包靠谱吗","createdAt":"2025-07-10T11:56:42"},{"id":"01986367-d3fd-708b-9050-a3b5e2a7bb6e","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":22452,"content":"李芹芹很阴风，研发小领导","createdAt":"2025-08-01T10:13:25"},{"id":"01986368-6df2-713f-b78f-52783ca160a4","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":21364,"content":"没太听懂哈哈哈","createdAt":"2025-08-01T10:14:05"},{"id":"01986370-53ff-710d-a43b-58715ff83716","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":22452,"content":"屎山代码，压缩开发时间，1，3，5或2，4，6加班，下班没有走的，这点风气很不正，8点动身走，你芹姐就会问你干的工作干完了吗？打电话问你，这回懂了吗？","createdAt":"2025-08-01T10:22:42"},{"id":"019863ad-fe34-716c-a13a-c030f07168ac","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":22913,"content":"最近进去的都是比自研还要低，不信你去试试","createdAt":"2025-08-01T11:30:03"},{"id":"019863b2-ac00-71b4-9196-62b0882df94a","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":22913,"content":"感觉就是外包啊，装什么自研","createdAt":"2025-08-01T11:35:10"},{"id":"019872e4-7e51-70ea-a06f-fe54ba5ab7db","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":21364,"content":"啧啧，，有点黑啊","createdAt":"2025-08-04T10:23:53"},{"id":"0198abc5-8714-7075-8cff-9e769bb3c02d","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":21119,"content":"这么多劝退帖了，再多少贴子，也叫不醒装睡的人。人家都有原始股的去了就等着剥削吧，这种公司都留不住1个月，你想想代码是啥样吧，去了背锅吗，加班下楼抽个烟放松放松都得给你开个小会","createdAt":"2025-08-15T11:28:25"},{"id":"0198abd7-c6e6-70f3-a68a-c139c45e9a50","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":21119,"content":"还有不信邪的呢，这家公司要是开缅甸去，就没那几个家族啥事了","createdAt":"2025-08-15T11:48:21"},{"id":"019b9d58-44b9-7337-b507-68a6aabcc8c6","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":2420,"content":"刚面过说是每月一个周六值班  我tm直接❓ 然后每周有两天固定加班到8点","createdAt":"2026-01-08T19:22:46"},{"id":"019b9d61-4f7d-736a-a002-d8b00d4078c5","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":2783,"content":"我们124到9点 没周六加班一天 哎","createdAt":"2026-01-08T19:32:38"},{"id":"019ba034-b8b3-7293-9e31-3934ff7f4e13","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":2420,"content":"有点工贼了 纯牛马","createdAt":"2026-01-09T08:42:48"},{"id":"019bfe0b-beb8-7365-8bdf-142bf3a3051a","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":21364,"content":"别去别去，全部都是长期出差，运气好的省内，运气不好的南方，一旦出去几乎就是无休，已润","createdAt":"2026-01-27T14:02:21"},{"id":"019c07bc-396f-7287-8888-863afd2d7bf0","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":22186,"content":"兄弟你是在本部吗","createdAt":"2026-01-29T11:11:41"}]